# SSH Keys Directory

This directory stores the generated SSH key pairs for accessing EC2 instances.

**Security Notice:** Key files in this directory should NOT be committed to version control.

Files in this directory:
- `hapi-loadtest-*.pem` - Private key for accessing HAPI FHIR EC2 instances

## Usage

After deploying the HapiStack, the private key will be automatically downloaded here.

To SSH into the HAPI instance:
```bash
ssh -i infra/keys/hapi-loadtest-<id>.pem ec2-user@<public-ip>
```

## Cleanup

Key files are automatically deleted when running the destroy script:
```bash
./infra/scripts/destroy-hapi.sh
```
